     fhir:Narrative.div "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><p>This code system http://fhir.org/guides/who/emc-cds/CodeSystem/emc-custom-codes-codes defines the following codes:</p><table class=\"codes\"><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b>Definition</b></td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.A.DE01<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46A.46DE01\"> </a></td><td>Unique identification</td><td>Unique identification</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.A.DE02<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46A.46DE02\"> </a></td><td>Unique Identification</td><td>Unique Identification</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.A.DE03<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46A.46DE03\"> </a></td><td>Child's Identity unknown/prefer to remain anonymous</td><td>Child's Identity unknown/prefer to remain anonymous</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.A.DE04<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46A.46DE04\"> </a></td><td>First name</td><td>First name</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.A.DE05<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46A.46DE05\"> </a></td><td>Middle Name</td><td>Middle Name</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.A.DE06<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46A.46DE06\"> </a></td><td>Last name</td><td>Last name</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.A.DE07<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46A.46DE07\"> </a></td><td>Visit date</td><td>Visit date</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.A.DE08<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46A.46DE08\"> </a></td><td>Date of birth</td><td>Date of birth</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.A.DE09<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46A.46DE09\"> </a></td><td>Time of Birth</td><td>Time of Birth</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.A.DE10<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46A.46DE10\"> </a></td><td>Age</td><td>Age</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.A.DE11<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46A.46DE11\"> </a></td><td>Date of Birth not known</td><td>Date of Birth not known</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.A.DE12<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46A.46DE12\"> </a></td><td>Provide an estimated age or estimated date of birth</td><td>Provide an estimated age or estimated date of birth</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.A.DE13<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46A.46DE13\"> </a></td><td>Estimated Age</td><td>Provide an estimated age or estimated date of birth - Estimated Age</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.A.DE14<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46A.46DE14\"> </a></td><td>Only know age in weeks/days/hours</td><td>Provide an estimated age or estimated date of birth - Only know age in weeks/days/hours</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.A.DE15<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46A.46DE15\"> </a></td><td>Estimated Date of Birth</td><td>Provide an estimated age or estimated date of birth - Estimated Date of Birth</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.A.DE16<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46A.46DE16\"> </a></td><td>Sex</td><td>Sex</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">female<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-female\"> </a></td><td>Female</td><td>Sex - Female</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">male<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-male\"> </a></td><td>Male</td><td>Sex - Male</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">unknown<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-unknown\"> </a></td><td>Not Specified</td><td>Sex - Not Specified</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.A.DE20<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46A.46DE20\"> </a></td><td>Address</td><td>Address</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.A.DE21<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46A.46DE21\"> </a></td><td>Primary Caregiver First Name</td><td>Primar