ltiple<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-multiple\"> </a></td><td>Two or more convulsions</td><td>Number of convulsions in this illness - Two or more convulsions</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.B7.DE07<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46B7.46DE07\"> </a></td><td>Convulsion(s) last 15 minutes or more</td><td>Convulsion(s) last 15 minutes or more</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.B7.DE08<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46B7.46DE08\"> </a></td><td>Unconscious or Lethargic</td><td>Unconscious or Lethargic</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.B7.DE09<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46B7.46DE09\"> </a></td><td>Not able to drink or breastfeed</td><td>Not able to drink or breastfeed</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.B7.DE10<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46B7.46DE10\"> </a></td><td>Vomiting</td><td>Vomiting</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">everything<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-everything\"> </a></td><td>Vomiting Everything</td><td>Vomiting - Vomiting Everything</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">not-everything<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-not-everything\"> </a></td><td>Vomiting but Not Everything</td><td>Vomiting - Vomiting but Not Everything</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">nothing<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-nothing\"> </a></td><td>No Vomiting</td><td>Vomiting - No Vomiting</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.B7.DE14<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46B7.46DE14\"> </a></td><td>Oral Fluid Test</td><td>Oral Fluid Test</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">everything<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-everything\"> </a></td><td>Vomits immediately / everything</td><td>Oral Fluid Test - Vomits immediately / everything</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">unable<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-unable\"> </a></td><td>Completely unable to drink</td><td>Oral Fluid Test - Completely unable to drink